        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I did several levels in my early 40's soloing the Forst Giant Scouts in GD.</P><P>I would park my pet in the pass to EW and fear kite them down the long valley.</P><P>I am not sure if this would work at your level to pull the wolves down there, because right at the entrance of the valley is a spawn point for both a static and a roaming giant. I'm not sure but you might be able to pull far enough on the side to not agro the giants and then you have a good long ways to fear kite down the valley. </P><P>I first tried killing them in the mountains close to Thurgadin but I got too many adds and there are a lot of Coldain runing around near there, but you might try there too.</P><P>Dryzza Souldrinker of Bunnies of Chaos<BR>52nd Level Heretic of Ayonae Ro<BR>Evil Mistress of the Dead<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
